<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="341" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,654,2013]" pageId="10" pageNumber="341">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1951,1977]" pageId="10" pageNumber="341">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[846,974,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="341">triacanthus</emphasis>
, referring to the three ventroapical spines of the valva.
</paragraph>
